    public class Spdy3ConnectorFactory
extends HttpsConnectorFactory
    Builds SPDY v3 connectors.

    Configuration Parameters:

    Name Default Description
    pushStrategy (none) The push strategy to use for server-initiated SPDY pushes.

    For more configuration parameters, see HttpsConnectorFactory.
